Version:        6.2.2101
Release:        0
Summary:        Automatic 3D tetrahedral mesh generator
License:        LGPL-2.1-only
Group:          Productivity/Graphics/CAD
URL:            https://ngsolve.org/
Source0:        netgen-%{version}.tar.xz
